        "content": "<p>alexcrichton <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/issues/12568#issuecomment-3888194711\">commented</a> on <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/issues/12568\">issue #12568</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>cc @badeend </p>\n</blockquote>",
